metadata.name: ETHDenver OKX Web3 Night NFT Pass #1
metadata.description: The side event NFT pass was just made available by OKX for the first time. You will qualify for a spot lottery once you become our NFT Ticket holder. To bring you a big surprise, OKX and well-known NFT initiatives like superpowersquad will provide the prize pool. NFT Pass holders will also be invited to join OKXWeb3's official VIP community channel, where holders receive more exclusive benefits in future events.
